and now we're going to add a riff,

00:00:56.208 --> 00:00:58.378
just like a guitar riff or a trombone riff

00:00:58.410 --> 00:01:01.017
with the right hand, it's made of two chords

00:01:08.413 --> 00:01:10.435
Here's both of them together

00:01:25.008 --> 00:01:29.562
That's the accompaniment, 
you'll have to play it over for a while to feel comfortable with it.

00:01:30.056 --> 00:01:34.181
