00:01:54.812 --> 00:01:58.579
with my accompanying figure, 
so we'll be mixing melody, accompaniment and bass

00:01:58.590 --> 00:02:00.283
as if there were three pianists

00:02:00.326 --> 00:02:02.787
don't forget, the piano is an orchestra!

00:03:03.548 --> 00:03:06.988
Afterwards, you can open up and improvise, 
which isn't easy,

00:03:07.028 --> 00:03:09.715
but there's always the blues scale:

00:03:10.868 --> 00:03:15.090
